While Bob is moving closer to my price range, his current offer of $1,150,000 is still below my guaranteed sale price from John ($1,200,000). It's unlikely Bob will meet or exceed John's offer at this point.  Therefore, it makes the most financial sense to cut off negotiations with Bob and sell to John.
